graph TD
    subgraph Widget Tree
        A[StatefulWidget]
        B[State]
    end

    A -->|Creates| B
    B -->|Holds mutable state| C[State Variables]
    B -->|Contains| D[build method]
    D -->|Returns| E[UI]
    C -->|Triggers setState| B

    subgraph User Interaction
        F[User Action]
        G[State Change]
    end

    F -->|Triggers| G
    G -->|Calls| C
    C -->|Updates State| B
    B -->|Calls| D
    D -->|Updates| E
